        "tab2_label": "Going Out",
        "tab2_subtitle": "Glasses' Moment",
        "tab2_description": "<p>Glasses on — just like any other pair. Walking down the street: \"You have a call at 10 with the Shanghai client.\" She didn't ask. Glasses just knew.</p>",
